New Improvements!

Room with 1 queen bed & private bath around corner in an older house with character. Sleeps up to 2. Includes access to great kitchen, living room & front deck. Close to downtown & all East Side bars & restaurants. Near bus stop. Easy street parking. Friendly dogs live in the house.
column9: Cozy room w/ private bath near DT; Summer UT
